Package: zion-miner
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: python3 (>= 3.8), python3-pip, systemd
Maintainer: ZION Development Team <dev@zion-testnet.org>
Description: ZION Real Mining Client - No Simulations Production Miner
 High-performance cryptocurrency miner for ZION TestNet 2.7.5.
 Features:
 - Real Stratum protocol mining (no simulations)
 - RandomX and YesCrypt algorithm support
 - Production-ready performance (500K+ H/s)
 - Automatic pool connection and share submission
 - Systemd service integration
 - Ubuntu 22.04/24.04 LTS support
 .
 This is the official ZION mining client for connecting to production
 mining pools and participating in ZION blockchain mining operations.
Homepage: https://github.com/estrelaisabellazion3/Zion-TestNet-2.7.5
